# NFT Marketplace

**Repository:** [https://github.com/Pynex/MarketplaceProject](https://github.com/Pynex/MarketplaceProject)

## Project Overview

An advanced NFT marketplace platform that enables users to create collections, mint NFTs, and trade them with integrated platform fees and promotional features. This project represents early startup experience and demonstrates comprehensive NFT ecosystem development.

## Key Features

### Core Marketplace Functionality

- **NFT Collection Creation** - Users can create custom NFT collections directly on the platform
- **Minting System** - Direct NFT minting with customizable metadata
- **Trading Platform** - Buy/sell functionality with market-driven pricing
- **Platform Fees** - Configurable commission system for marketplace sustainability

### Advanced Trading Features

- **Batch Purchasing** - Efficient multi-NFT acquisition in single transaction
- **Promotional System** - Special minting bonuses for purchasers
- **Collection Management** - Comprehensive collection administration tools
- **Marketplace Analytics** - Trading volume and activity tracking

## ðŸ›  Technical Implementation

### Technology Stack

- **Framework:** Foundry
- **Language:** Solidity ^0.8.x
- **Testing:** Forge (Foundry's testing framework)
- **Libraries:**
  - OpenZeppelin Contracts (ERC721, Access Control, Security)
  - Custom marketplace logic and fee distribution

## NFT Collection Features

### Dynamic Collection Creation

- **On-Chain Deployment** - New ERC721 contracts created per collection
- **Customizable Metadata** - Flexible attribute and trait systems
- **Creator Royalties** - Automatic royalty distribution to creators
- **Collection Branding** - Custom names, symbols, and descriptions

### Minting Mechanics

- **Metadata Management** - IPFS integration for decentralized storage
- **Batch Minting** - Efficient multi-NFT creation
- **Access Control** - Creator permissions and minting rights

## Economic Model

### Fee Structure

- **Platform Fees** - Configurable percentage on all sales
- **Creator Royalties** - Ongoing revenue for original creators
- **Gas Optimization** - Minimized transaction costs

## Testing & Quality Assurance

### Comprehensive Test Suite

- **100% Code Coverage** - Every function and edge case tested
- **Unit Tests** - Individual contract function validation
- **Integration Tests** - Multi-contract workflow testing
- **Fuzz Testing** - Random input validation with Foundry

### Security Testing

- **Access Control Tests** - Permission system validation
- **Reentrancy Protection** - Safe external call patterns
- **Input Validation** - Comprehensive parameter checking

